{"tid":1668813,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【NBA揭幕戰】央視封殺改播軍運會 騰訊有得睇偷雞加月費","createTime":"2019-10-22T08:00:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-22T14:19:31.000Z","uid":130626,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"34f2abf5cff9538b8ad2583372058f795f583deb","tid":1668813,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T08:00:26.000Z","msg":"美國NBA揭幕戰香港時間明早8時在洛杉磯史達普斯中心上演湖人作客快艇，但火箭總經理莫利（Daryl Morey）月初聲援香港反送中運動後，NBA已遭內地官方打壓。明日兩場賽事塘鵝對速龍、湖人對快艇，後日將會安排11場比賽，各隊伍也陸續亮相。央視近日更新節目表，確定不會轉播NBA揭幕戰，繼續封殺NBA。騰訊體育則靜悄悄將會員月費加價至88元人民幣（約97港元）。<br />\n<br />\n央視CCTV5頻道，明早直播節目主要是第七屆軍人運動會，到了周四（24日），CCTV5依然主要直播軍人運動會，甚至軍運會為錄播節目也不直播NBA賽事，態度說非常強硬。往年，同一時候央視都會播放各種宣傳片，幫NBA進行熱身，也提前預告會直播的比賽和場次，但是如今這些宣傳悄然消失。<br />\n現在央視已經確認不轉播NBA揭幕戰，常規賽何時復播仍然是未知之數，現在NBA一共有30支球隊一起在央視「消失」不見了。沒有了央視的直播支持，NBA可以說損失慘重，如今已經不少中國品牌與NBA中止合作。對NBA來說，現在損失已經無可避免，接下來等待他們的恐怕會是一系列問題的出現。<br />\n<br />\nNBA常規賽揭幕戰，除了官方電視台央視不會直播，在內地網絡平台仍然可以看到兩場賽事，而勝訊會員突然將月費由60元（約66港元）加至88元，引起不少球迷反感。<br />\n明早兩場重頭戲包括香港時間早上８時塘鵝對速龍，以及早上10時30分揭幕戰湖人對快艇，除了騰訊體育的選擇之外，新浪體育也會進行直播，但連結CCTV5的直播吧、虎撲等籃球論壇，則無法收看有關賽事。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191022/large/1571722806_0229.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191022%2Flarge%2F1571722806_0229.jpg&h=cd787a13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20191022/60181470\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191022%2F60181470&d=kAMrkm0lh8tAzahNx%2FKaSEPclXdXKQfB%2FlJdEd6ZkMI%3D&h=71b7cec4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191022%2F60181470&h=2090c92d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20191022/60181470</a>"},{"pid":"0c5ccb30e75820980859c3931b820f9179ee3dca","tid":1668813,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T08:01:28.000Z","msg":"【文宣學堂】警完美示範「核彈都唔割」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1667502\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1667502</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n以後見到有割席分化post，我地應即貼上巴打提議嘅金句：<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf78e295a6d285c471a8b1dd1d1a26c62e6a791a","tid":1668813,"uid":97451,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T08:03:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e9c4c47e0e5a058c651fecd183a2f13ffca7df06","tid":1668813,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T08:14:55.000Z","msg":"係咪會全場都著stand with Hong Kong tee?"},{"pid":"dab40489f4a2ac2e63726e4443381e284661aa4f","tid":1668813,"uid":35211,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T08:18:00.000Z","msg":"封乜殺NBA<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 怕D Stand with Hong Kong T-shirt咋"},{"pid":"b6edb97322eb73bef84a1a310637ce3e5fd0df0e","tid":1668813,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T08:42:20.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e0cf45db97fc6edb6187b554818552657286f24","tid":1668813,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T08:58:51.000Z","msg":"睇解放軍跑步"},{"pid":"1c1403092d5d0dc0e72c439228cdb17ff0260c5e","tid":1668813,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6e0cf45db97fc6edb6187b554818552657286f24","tid":1668813,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T08:58:51.000Z","msg":"睇解放軍跑步"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T09:34:45.000Z","msg":"愛國就係要睇呢d節目架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal